SECOND REGULAR SESSION
HOUSE BILL NO. 3033
103RD GENERAL ASSEMBLY
INTRODUCED BY REPRESENTATIVE COOK.
6624H.01I JOSEPH ENGLER, Chief Clerk
AN ACT
To amend chapter 227, RSMo, by adding thereto one new section relating to the renaming of
a roadway.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the state of Missouri, as follows:
Section A. Chapter 227, RSMo, is amended by adding thereto one new section, to be
2 known as section 227.880, to read as follows:
227.880. Shafer Road from its intersection with Highway 63 in Texas County
2 north to its intersection with Highway 63 in Phelps County shall be renamed "State
3 Route 137" and no political subdivision shall designate such roadway otherwise.
✔
EXPLANATION — Matter enclosed in bold-faced brackets [thus] in the above bill is not enacted and is
intended to be omitted from the law. Matter in bold-face type in the above bill is proposed language.

